#

Ambrosia Apple Crisp

60 min
$10
220 kcal
Difficulty: 20%
Servings: 6

Allergens:

glutendairy

Dietary Tags:

vegetariannut-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dessert

Tags:

desserteasybaked

Description

A warm and comforting dessert featuring sweet Ambrosia apples baked under a crunchy oat topping, perfect for any occasion.

Ingredients

  • ambrosia apples: 4, peeled and sliced
  • brown sugar: 1/2 cup
  • old-fashioned oats: 1 cup
  • all-purpose flour: 1/2 cup
  • unsalted butter: 1/4 cup, melted
  • cinnamon: 1 teaspoon
  • nutmeg: 1/4 teaspoon
  • salt: 1/4 teaspoon
